        "content": "<p>I'm not entirely sure what is going on there. IIRC I tested that code on a VisionFive 2 as well, but with a super old kernel, so something might have changed.</p>\n<p>If I'm not mistaken docker filters the allowed syscalls, and it might be that that one isn't allowed. (This is just a wild guess)</p>\n<p>I'll try to reproduce that locally</p>",
        "id": 442592417,
        "sender_full_name": "Afonso Bordado",
        "timestamp": 1717524291
